<h2>About Us</h2>
<p>Welcome to Calm&Connect! We are a platform dedicated to providing accessible and anonymous psychiatric consultancy services to individuals seeking mental health support. Our mission is to help individuals manage anxiety, stress, and other mental health challenges, one step at a time.</p>

<h3>Our Mission</h3>
<p>At Calm&Connect, we believe in offering individuals a safe space where they can seek guidance, without judgment or barriers. Our mission is to provide a compassionate and secure platform for those dealing with mental health issues, ensuring they have access to professional help at their convenience.</p>

<h3>Our Values</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Confidentiality:</strong> We respect the privacy of our users and ensure all consultations remain anonymous.</li>
    <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> We aim to provide mental health services to anyone who needs them, regardless of location or background.</li>
    <li><strong>Compassion:</strong> We approach every interaction with care, empathy, and a deep understanding of the challenges our users face.</li>
</ul>

